    public class PatchProcessSignalingRandom
extends PatchProcessSignaling
    Extension of PatchProcessSignaling for random EGFR signaling.

    PatchModuleSignalingRandom randomly sets the migratory flag based on MIGRATORY_PROBABILITY.
